spanGrp.span: NHK speaks about the political structure of the Tabaq community. He speaks about the chiefs and the Kujurs (= Arabic term for Tabaq /kwii/, i.e. a person who is involuntarily possessed by spirit/s respected by the Tabaq people, and who send their messages through the /kwii/). And he then speaks about the relationship between the religious/spiritual power and the political/legislative power in the Tabaq community.
Panasonic Lumix DMC-GH2K (set to AVCHD(1080i), FSH), plus external stereo microphone (Rode Stereo VideoMic) & windshield
Zoom H4n (set to WAV, 44.1Hz/16bit) + Beyerdynamic M 58 microfone
